    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir</salute></opener>

                <p>What is the institution, duty, arms &amp;c of the city guard? <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0299">Maitland</title></bibl> is silent. Where
                    stands the <placeName ref="pl1041">new episcopal chapel</placeName>? how far is
                    completed? answers speedily to these queries will much oblige</p>
                <closer><salute>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">T. Pennant</persName></signed>
                <dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> Oct<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        17<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi> 1775.</dateline></closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>To</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> George Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom house</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburgh</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
